{
  "stem": "1491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I say, I don't have-- what about?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I always sat and talked with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Spock was my guidance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You Know, I didn't know, which people take for granted things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like my best girlfriend had a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was earning nice living later on when I learned the trade and everything, that you go visiting someone that has a new baby, you have to bring a gift.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So many things what you take for granted which comes natural to people, we didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I personally didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on when the boy got big-- this was the first baby I ever held in my arms-- I used to say, I was so stupid.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could have afford, but I didn't know that you have to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so many things that people take for granted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I remember I went to work in the office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I called my girlfriend, I said, how do I use a staple remover?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Which to every child, it's normal because they go to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they work in the school offices.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They helping out the teachers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't have all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was deprived of everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever I did, I did by force really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I tried to learn, but we were busy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only six years, I would say eight years out of our life, living in the displaced camps, going through the pogroms, and even coming to United States where it's a free country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we struggled till we came to something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Which really people take things so much-- so many things might look stupid, she doesn't know that.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
